  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase emphasizing the Tide stage's Sample-and-Hold shape. ORBWEAVE's trefoil knot topology generates internal phase relationships that, when filtered through Tide's S&H LFO at 0.25 Hz, create stepped spectral windows — as if the knot is rotating into and out of different aspects of itself. Fathom at Character 0.4 neutral. Drift at 4 voices. Reef at moderate size 0.5 and density 0.6. The S&H Tide is the defining feature: it makes topology audible as rhythm.",
